  <p class="en">The <a href="/en/blog/200-week-moving-average">200-week moving average</a> (~$61,300) was briefly broken twice — in early June and again on CPI day — and reclaimed both times. Given that all three past cycle bottoms formed near or just below this line, we're clearly in a meaningful zone.</p>
